title: Around The Globe - Must See Places in North America
description:
Around The Globe - Must See Places in North America: North America Travel Guide for Kids (Children's Explore the World Books)


Go around North America and learn about the best places to visit even before you have your papers ready. This virtual tour of such vast land will help you plan out your itinerary and see the most recommended places. Your child can also use this picture book to learn about geography, races and culture too
